{
  "stem": "7455.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And under the circumstances, that was the only thing to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Laura studied Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And she-- she ran to the mailman constantly for correspondence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "He told her about the beauty of the land, how the main concentration is on the youth, because they are the future.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "It's beautiful, and you'll see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "We'll have a good life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And she had tears, crying, hoping.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And then, without warning, the war broke out and the Russians marched in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And Russia is isolated from the world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "It's an iron curtain.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "She tried to smuggle out through the border, and she was caught, pushed back, sent back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "Her heart broke, because she knew that she'll never see him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And after some time elapsed, correspondence stopped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "If something happened to Laura, she-- she knew she's not going to see him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And she loved him very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And my father felt very guilty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "He should have-- he could have sold the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "We could have found means to send them together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "But under the circumstances then, that was the rational thing to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "Had he have known what will come ahead, nothing would have stopped him to send his daughter with her husband, together.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "Laura's heart was broken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And now my father, when he knew that there's a chance for Christian documents-- she had a perky nose, blonde.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "She did not look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "So-- so he knew that he must-- she must go to her husband.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And he-- we have to give whatever we have.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "But Laura said, but you're going to be starving if you give away for our document.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "He said, somebody has to survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "Somebody should tell what was done to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "We thought there'll no Jews left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "And your husband is waiting.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
